  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd. \u0b95\u0bcb\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b88\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Jaffna. Those involved in the robbery incident were arrested at Koppai police station",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna District Crime Prevention Police have arrested 10 people including the main suspect and the jeweler shop owner and accomplices involved in the theft and robbery of three houses in Koppai Police Division.",
        "A complaint was lodged at Koppai Police Station regarding the theft of gold jewellery, valuable mobile phones, cooking gas cylinder and two-wheeler by breaking into two houses under the bed in Konda in the months of May and June.",
        "Also, in another house, the gold jewelry worn by the woman was hacked. A complaint was filed at Koppai Police Station in this regard.",
        "The District Crime Prevention Police headed by Inspector General of Police Nicholas Francis, who operates under the Jaffna Senior Superintendent of Police, conducted investigations into the incidents.",
        "The main suspect from Chunnagam area was arrested in connection with the incidents.",
        "In the investigations carried out against him, 9 other persons were arrested as accomplices as pawnbrokers, belonging to Kilinochchi Sunnagadatha and the owner of a jewelery shop in Jaffapanam.",
        "It is noteworthy that the police said that the main suspect was addicted to drugs and was involved in robbery and theft and was wanted by the police."
      ],
